<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201019/baf02a0e29454742bac2af27e558822a.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《红军谷》120×120cm</span></img></p>
