<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201019/b308eb293c2340cab9f8827b8d7f1f85.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《寒山石极》68×68cm</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201019/4bf8279596704236babc5a99665b8db7.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《鹅岭长泉》180×98cm</span></img></p>
