<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201019/50008e76690f496e9eb8c84011e49c26.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">理习忠《故乡之冬》120x120cm</span></img></p>
